videos.headline: UNLV jumps ahead on 5-yard TD run
videos.description: Tyleek Collins takes the jet sweep and shoots through an opening to put the Rebels on top 14-7.

videos.headline: UNLV extends lead with 28-yard QB keeper
videos.description: QB Armani Rogers turns on the jets and beats the defense to the end zone, giving the Rebels a 21-10 lead.

videos.headline: UNLV QB throws 22-yard TD pass before halftime
videos.description: Armani Rogers throws a strike to WR Darren Woods Jr., who drags a defender into the end zone and puts the rebels up by 28.

videos.headline: UNLV RB jukes defender for TD
videos.description: Lexington Thomas uses a nasty spin move to find paydirt and give UNLV a 45-10 lead.

videos.headline: UNLV pours it on with easy 3-yard TD pass
videos.description: Armani Rogers hits a wide open Tyleek Collins in the flat, who walks into the end zone to make it 52-17 Rebels.
